{"remainingRequest":"D:\\学校学习文件\\web技术\\github-new\\pethome\\pethome0614\\pethome-main\\pethome-main\\pet-home\\frontend\\node_modules\\vue-loader\\lib\\index.js??vue-loader-options!D:\\学校学习文件\\web技术\\github-new\\pethome\\pethome0614\\pethome-main\\pethome-main\\pet-home\\frontend\\src\\views\\Home.vue?vue&type=script&lang=js","dependencies":[{"path":"D:\\学校学习文件\\web技术\\github-new\\pethome\\pethome0614\\pethome-main\\pethome-main\\pet-home\\frontend\\src\\views\\Home.vue","mtime":1782219442787},{"path":"D:\\学校学习文件\\web技术\\github-new\\pethome\\pethome0614\\pethome-main\\pethome-main\\pet-home\\frontend\\node_modules\\cache-loader\\dist\\cjs.js","mtime":1781710963447},{"path":"D:\\学校学习文件\\web技术\\github-new\\pethome\\pethome0614\\pethome-main\\pethome-main\\pet-home\\frontend\\node_modules\\vue-loader\\lib\\index.js","mtime":1781710966904}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":[{"type":"Buffer","data":"base64:"},{"version":3,"sources":["Home.vue"],"names":[],"mappings":";AAwEA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA;AACA","file":"Home.vue","sourceRoot":"src/views","sourcesContent":["<template>\r\n  <div class=\"home-page\">\r\n    <!-- 轮播图区域 - 纯图片 -->\r\n    <div class=\"banner-section\">\r\n      <el-carousel :interval=\"4000\" height=\"800px\" indicator-position=\"outside\">\r\n        <el-carousel-item v-for=\"(item, index) in banners\" :key=\"index\">\r\n          <div class=\"banner-item\" :style=\"{ backgroundImage: `url(${item.image})` }\"></div>\r\n        </el-carousel-item>\r\n      </el-carousel>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- 品牌介绍卡片（轮播图后面，7张图片前面） -->\r\n    <div class=\"brand-intro-section\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"brand-card\" @click=\"showBrandDialog = true\">\r\n          <div class=\"brand-icon\">🐾</div>\r\n          <div class=\"brand-text\">\r\n            <h3>宠物健康，从日常护理开始</h3>\r\n            <p>点击了解品牌故事 →</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- 特色图片展示区（7张图片纵向排列） -->\r\n    <div class=\"feature-grid-section\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\r\n          <div class=\"feature-item\" v-for=\"(item, index) in featureImages\" :key=\"index\">\r\n            <img :src=\"item.image\" :alt=\"'特色图片' + (index + 1)\">\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- 品牌理念展示 -->\r\n    <div class=\"philosophy-section\">\r\n      <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"philosophy-grid\">\r\n          <div class=\"philosophy-item\" v-for=\"(item, index) in philosophies\" :key=\"index\">\r\n            <div class=\"philosophy-icon\">{{ item.icon }}</div>\r\n            <h4>{{ item.title }}</h4>\r\n            <p>{{ item.desc }}</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- 品牌介绍弹窗 -->\r\n    <el-dialog\r\n        title=\"🐾 宠物家品牌故事\"\r\n        :visible.sync=\"showBrandDialog\"\r\n        width=\"700px\"\r\n        :before-close=\"handleDialogClose\"\r\n        class=\"brand-dialog\"\r\n    >\r\n      <div class=\"dialog-content\">\r\n        <p>宠物家是深受宠友信赖的品牌，持续引领宠物健康护理行业标准化建设，在行业领先实现了数字化体验，并在超一线城市实现护理型直营门店的快速规模化发展，用户数量及服务体量遥遥领先。</p>\r\n        <br />\r\n        <p>宠物健康，是长久、高质量人宠陪伴的前提，宠物家倡导\"健康，从日常护理开始\"，专注于宠物健康护理服务、保健服务、疾病预防服务、日用全品类商品零售、宠物药品零售、诊疗等业务，践行让宠物身心健康、延缓衰老，宠友快乐养宠的服务理念。</p>\r\n        <br />\r\n        <p>作为国内领先实现\"宠物产业互联网化\"的品牌，宠物家着力数字化建设，线上强效率，线下重体验。并依托于宠物个性化数据，深度挖掘用户需求，提供精准健康护理服务，定制个性化养宠解决方案，是率先实现\"千宠千面\"的数字化企业，满足宠友对于精细化科学养宠的追求，并深入影响用户心智，为品牌伙伴在产品研发及市场投入过程中提供精准赋能。</p>\r\n        <br />\r\n        <p>推出\"付费会员制\"，为Pet'em Prime宠物家会员提供专属会员服务。目前年提供超200万只次满意服务，直营护理型门店覆盖北京深圳上海核心区域，拥有可持续发展的人才建设体系，目前专业宠物护理师近2000名。创新研发定制化护理项目，目前仅单品种宠物即拥有数十项包含日常保养、抗衰老在内的健康护理SKU，实现了规范化、规模化、创新性发展。我们不断拓展边际，宠大夫药房运营中、宠大夫诊疗等即将启动，将致力于提供全生命周期健康养宠解决方案。</p>\r\n        <br />\r\n        <p style=\"font-weight: 600; color: #ff9f43;\">我们将一直秉承\"选择宠物家，尽可放心\"的品牌承诺，让宠友轻松养宠，快乐陪伴。</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </el-dialog>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script>\r\nexport default {\r\n  name: 'Home',\r\n  data() {\r\n    return {\r\n      showBrandDialog: false,\r\n      banners: [\r\n        { image: '/images/home-bg1.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-bg2.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-bg3.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-bg4.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-bg5.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-bg6.png' }\r\n      ],\r\n      // 7张特色图片\r\n      featureImages: [\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs1.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs2.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs3.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs4.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs5.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs6.png' },\r\n        { image: '/images/home-zs7.png' }\r\n      ],\r\n      philosophies: [\r\n        {\r\n          icon: '🏥',\r\n          title: '专业护理',\r\n          desc: '标准化服务流程，近2000名专业护理师'\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          icon: '📊',\r\n          title: '数字化体验',\r\n          desc: '线上强效率，线下重体验，千宠千面'\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          icon: '🏪',\r\n          title: '直营门店',\r\n          desc: '覆盖北京、深圳、上海核心区域'\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          icon: '💎',\r\n          title: '会员专享',\r\n          desc: '付费会员制，享受专属服务权益'\r\n        }\r\n      ]\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  methods: {\r\n    handleDialogClose() {\r\n      this.showBrandDialog = false\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style scoped>\r\n.home-page {\r\n  background: #faf8f5;\r\n  min-height: 100vh;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.container {\r\n  max-width: 1200px;\r\n  margin: 0 auto;\r\n  padding: 0 24px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== 轮播图 - 纯图片 ===== */\r\n.banner-section {\r\n  margin-bottom: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.banner-item {\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n  background-size: cover;\r\n  background-position: center;\r\n  background-repeat: no-repeat;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== 品牌介绍卡片（轮播图后面） ===== */\r\n.brand-intro-section {\r\n  padding: 20px 0;\r\n  background: #fff;\r\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ebe5;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-card {\r\n  display: flex;\r\n  align-items: center;\r\n  gap: 20px;\r\n  padding: 20px 30px;\r\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8f0, #fff0e0);\r\n  border-radius: 16px;\r\n  cursor: pointer;\r\n  transition: all 0.3s;\r\n  border: 1px solid #ffd4a0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-card:hover {\r\n  transform: translateY(-2px);\r\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,159,67,0.2);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-icon {\r\n  font-size: 48px;\r\n  flex-shrink: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-text h3 {\r\n  font-size: 20px;\r\n  color: #333;\r\n  margin-bottom: 4px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-text p {\r\n  color: #ff9f43;\r\n  font-size: 14px;\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== 特色图片展示区（7张图片纵向排列） ===== */\r\n.feature-grid-section {\r\n  padding: 20px 0;\r\n  background: #fff;\r\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ebe5;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.feature-grid {\r\n  display: flex;\r\n  flex-direction: column;\r\n  gap: 16px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.feature-item {\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  max-width: 1500px;\r\n  margin: 0 auto;\r\n  border-radius: 14px;\r\n  overflow: hidden;\r\n  background: #f5f0eb;\r\n  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;\r\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.feature-item:hover {\r\n  transform: scale(1.008);\r\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,159,67,0.15);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.feature-item img {\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  height: auto;\r\n  display: block;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== 品牌理念 ===== */\r\n.philosophy-section {\r\n  padding: 48px 0;\r\n  background: #faf8f5;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.philosophy-grid {\r\n  display: grid;\r\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\r\n  gap: 24px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.philosophy-item {\r\n  background: #fff;\r\n  border-radius: 16px;\r\n  padding: 30px 20px;\r\n  text-align: center;\r\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\r\n  transition: all 0.3s;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.philosophy-item:hover {\r\n  transform: translateY(-4px);\r\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,159,67,0.12);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.philosophy-icon {\r\n  font-size: 40px;\r\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.philosophy-item h4 {\r\n  font-size: 18px;\r\n  color: #333;\r\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.philosophy-item p {\r\n  font-size: 14px;\r\n  color: #888;\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n  line-height: 1.6;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== 弹窗样式 ===== */\r\n.brand-dialog >>> .el-dialog {\r\n  border-radius: 20px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-dialog >>> .el-dialog__header {\r\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ebe5;\r\n  padding: 20px 24px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.brand-dialog >>> .el-dialog__title {\r\n  font-size: 20px;\r\n  color: #333;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.dialog-content {\r\n  max-height: 400px;\r\n  overflow-y: auto;\r\n  padding-right: 8px;\r\n  font-size: 14px;\r\n  line-height: 1.8;\r\n  color: #555;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.dialog-content::-webkit-scrollbar {\r\n  width: 4px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.dialog-content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\r\n  background: #ffd4a0;\r\n  border-radius: 2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* ===== 响应式 ===== */\r\n@media (max-width: 992px) {\r\n  .philosophy-grid {\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .feature-item {\r\n    max-width: 100%;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\r\n  .banner-section {\r\n    height: 300px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .banner-item {\r\n    height: 300px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .brand-card {\r\n    flex-direction: column;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    padding: 20px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .philosophy-grid {\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n    gap: 16px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .feature-grid {\r\n    gap: 12px;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\r\n  .banner-section {\r\n    height: 220px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .banner-item {\r\n    height: 220px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .philosophy-grid {\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n    gap: 12px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .philosophy-item {\r\n    padding: 20px 16px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .philosophy-icon {\r\n    font-size: 30px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .feature-grid {\r\n    gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</style>"]}]}